International:
   Hong Kong Retail Sales Rise
The value increase follows growth of 19% in November, 20%
in October and 26% in September.
   According to seasonally unadjusted figures, sales were up
16% in December from November, measured both by volume and
value. The best growth in December from a year earlier was
recorded in sales of jewelry, watches and valuable gifts,
which were up 42% by value and 48% in volume terms.